  "text": "Does each entity have an individual mind, body, spirit complex totality, or do a number of entities share the same mind, body, spirit complex totality. I am Ra. Both of these statements are correct given the appropriate time space conditions. Each entity has its totality and at the point at which a planetary entity becomes a social memory complex the totality of this union of entities also has its over soul and its social memory complex totality as resource. As always, the sum spiritually speaking is greater than the sum of its parts, so that the oversoul of a social memory complex is not the sum of the oversouls of its member entities, but operates upon the way of what we have called squares and what we grasp you prefer to call doubling.",
